10 4. Students who have received intensive reading intervention
11 for two (2) or more years but still demonstrate a deficiency in
12 reading, and who were previously retained in kindergarten, first,
13 second, or third grade for a total of two (2) years. No student
14 shall be retained twice in third grade.
